@BookToneApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5010

### Get book tone recommendation
GET {{BookToneApi_HostAddress}}/api/BookToneRecommendations?BookTitle=The Great Gatsby&BookAuthor=F. Scott Fitzgerald&Genres=Fiction&Genres=Classic&Genres=Drama
Accept: application/json

### Get book tone recommendation for a technical book
GET {{BookToneApi_HostAddress}}/api/BookToneRecommendations?BookTitle=Clean Code&BookAuthor=Robert C. Martin&Genres=Technology&Genres=Programming&Genres=Education
Accept: application/json

### Get book tone recommendation for a mystery book
GET {{BookToneApi_HostAddress}}/api/BookToneRecommendations?BookTitle=The Da Vinci Code&BookAuthor=Dan Brown&Genres=Mystery&Genres=Thriller&Genres=Fiction
Accept: application/json

### Update book tone recommendation feedback
PUT {{BookToneApi_HostAddress}}/api/BookToneRecommendations/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "feedback": 1,
  "tone": "Formal"
}
